sub_title: Sand Artist events & Live show, Arts, Entertainment
summary:
Andrew Armanyous is a young Egyptian painter with a world-wide intellect. He discovered his artistic talent at the age of seven when he was re-painting pictures and artifacts in the house where he was encouraged by the parents, and strange in this age he found his personality and psychological comfort in this art.
The first difficult challenge when he was prevented from entering the exam for the Faculty of Fine Arts which he did not give up his dream and decided to pursue personal efforts.

Diversity and innovation was part of the challenge. He decided to leave the traditional tools in drawing and to use nature materials in drawing using the sand of the sea, to go to imaginations and depth in the art of sand with the use of light reflection, he felt the spirit of excitement which was the cause of inspiration and the novel story which the history will mention over the years.

After years of work, Andrew has been able to imitate the hearts of millions of viewers around the world and frame dramatic artistic scenes that mimic the human reality of sand art through the use of sound and lighting techniques.
